---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contatto — Mas du Chanoine" description="Contattate il Mas du Chanoine per una richiesta di disponibilità o prenotazione a Saint-Paul de Vence." lang="it">
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-28 px-4 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-100"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 text-accent-600 font-light">Contattaci</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary-900">Contatto</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-6">Richieste di disponibilità</h2>
          <p class="text-primary-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Per ogni richiesta di disponibilità o prenotazione, non esitate a contattarci per telefono, email o WhatsApp.</p>
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <div><h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-1">Telefono</h3><a href="tel:+33627271649" class="text-accent-600 text-lg font-medium">+33 (0)6 27 27 16 49</a></div>
            <div><h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-1">Email</h3><a href="mailto:pascale@masduchanoine.com" class="text-accent-600 text-lg font-medium">pascale@masduchanoine.com</a></div>
            <div><h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-1">Indirizzo</h3><address class="not-italic text-primary-600"><p>831 chemin de la Bastide Rouge</p><p>06570 Saint-Paul de Vence</p><p>Costa Azzurra, Francia</p></address></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-accent-600 text-white rounded-sm p-6 md:p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold mb-3">Prenotate direttamente</h3>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mb-4">Potete anche prenotare direttamente tramite il nostro motore di prenotazione online.</p>
            <a href="https://masduchanoine.thais-hotel.com/hotel/website/reservations.php?lang=it" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary bg-white text-primary-900 hover:bg-primary-100">Prenota ora</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2885.6!2d7.0584!3d43.6951!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12cdd1f0c5e1e29f%3A0x5f5b5b5b5b5b5b5b!2sMas%20du%20Chanoine!5e0!3m2!1sit!2sfr!4v1" width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen loading="lazy" title="Posizione del Mas du Chanoine"></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
